    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, keeping it spotless and running like a total dream. It\u2019s seriously stunning and ready for its next big adventure. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
