    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional, museum-quality E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six. This specimen is mechanically pristine, having undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite including a VANOS system overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers short, precise throws, channeling power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated M-Variable differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring peak lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. With original paint showing zero imperfections and a cabin preserved in its factory state, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of BMW M-division engineering for the purist collector.",
